get_metric_header(25.10)                              get_metric_header(25.10)

Name  get_metric_header  -  Returns  the  metric header information set by the
       set_metric_header command
Syntax
Parameters -id <db_id> Specifies the database ID. Data_type: string,  optional
       -name  <header>  <_name  > Specifies the name of the header. Data_type:
       string, required -help Outputs a brief description that  includes  type
       and default information for each get_metric_header parameter. For a de-
       tailed  description  of  the command and all of its parameters, use the
       man command: man get_metric_header
